Package me.alb_i986.selenium.tinafw.tasks

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WebTask
    A WebTask is supposed to simulate a user interaction with the SUT.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseWebTask
    Abstract WebTask responsible for knowing the 'who', i.e.
    CompositeWebTask
    A WebTask made up of many supposedly small (sub-)tasks, which in turn may be CompositeWebTask's too.
    ImLoggedInBase
    Concrete subclasses must define the method `getPageClassToLoad` which needs to return a concrete LoginPage.
    ManualNavigationWebTask
    A WebTask encapsulating a manual navigation step.
    MyBrowserIsOpen
    Task that opens the browser.
    NavigationWebTask
    A WebTask encapsulating a step for navigating to a LoadablePage.
    NullTask
    Task that does nothing.
    OrWebTask
    A CompositeWebTask which chains subtasks in a logical OR.
    WebTasks
    Static class providing factory methods for building instances of WebTask's.
    WebTasks.BDD
    Static class providing factory methods for creating BDD-style tasks: givens whens thens.
